e or nothing from his successes. They mainly confirm him in his mistakes  while his failures  on the other hand  are priceless experiences in that they not only open up the way to a deeper truth  but force him to change his views and methods.', 28934, 0), (401386, 'Failure ... is  in a sense  the highway to success  inasmuch as every discovery of what is false leads us to seek earnestly after what is true  and every fresh experience points out some form of error which we shall afterward carefully avoid.', 191, 0), (401387, 'We need to teach a highly educated person that it is not a disgrace to fail and that he must analyze every failure to find its cause. He must learn how to fail intelligently  for failing is one of the greatest arts of the world.', 41716, 0), (401388, 'When a man is pushed  tormented  defeated  he has a chance to learn something  he has been put on his wits  on his manhood  he has gained the facts  learned his ignorance  is cured of the insanity of conceit  has got moderation and real skill.', 760, 0), (401389, 'There are no mistakes. The events we bring upon ourselves  no matter how unpleasant  are necessary in order to learn what we need to learn  whatever steps we take  they''re necessary to reach the places we''ve chosen to go.', 424, 0), (401390, 'Failure is instructive. The person who really thinks learns quite as much from his failures as from his successes.', 2575, 0), (401391, 'Failure is a school in which the truth always grows strong.', 2175, 0), (401392, 'The important thing is to learn a lesson every time you lose.', 63558, 0), (401393, 'It''s good to fail now and again - you learn a lot more out of failure than you do out of success.', 40314, 0), (401394, 'One of the reasons mature people stop learning is that they become less and less willing to risk failure.', 11471, 0), (401395, 'Through failure  we learn a lesson in humility which is probably needed  painful though it is.', 4747, 0), (401396, 'A failure is a man who has blundered  but is not able to cash in the experience.', 4, 0), (401397, 'Like success  failure is many things to many people. With Positive Mental Attitude  failure is a learning experience  a rung on the ladder  a plateau at which to get your thoughts in order and prepare to try again.', 3433, 0), (401398, 'Disappointment is the nurse of wisdom.', 62387, 0), (401399, 'When you make a mistake  don''t look back at it long. Take the reason of the thing into your mind  and then look forward. Mistakes are lessons of wisdom. The past cannot be changed. The future is yet in your power.', 63559, 0), (401400, 'What can any of us do with his talent but try to develop his vision  so that through frequent failures we may learn better what we have missed in the past.', 8629, 0);
